FBIS4-11376 "drlat080_l_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-080 Daily Report 25 Apr 1994 Bolivia Official: State of Siege Not To Be Implemented Official: State of Siege Not To Be Implemented PY2504180694 La Paz Television Nacional Network in Spanish 1700 GMT 25 Apr 94 PY2504180694 La Paz Television Nacional Network Spanish BFN [Text] According to Fides Press Agency, Minister of the Presidency Carlos Sanchez Berzain reiterated that the government will not implement a state of siege. COB [Bolivian Labor Federation] Executive Secretary Oscar Salas, however, has asserted that the country already is living under a virtual state of siege taking into account the measures taken so far by the government of the coalition headed by the National Revolutionary Movement.
